{"tid":1537780,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟乜撚嘢叫香港人加油你地明唔撚明啊","createTime":"2019-09-04T04:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T05:30:43.000Z","uid":55038,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"52b95e2fda73f30cd533aa66209434ad3bf2960c","tid":1537780,"uid":55038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:57:21.000Z","msg":"屌佢老味連登仔有時真心憨鳩<br />\n你地知唔撚知咩台灣有樣嘢叫國安法<br />\n知唔撚知台灣唔係歐美等地嘅強國<br />\n屌你老味人地肯企出黎出聲已經好撚勇啦憨鳩<br />\n收票？蔡英文講完依句幾撚多廢老會反對佢？唔係以為台灣冇廢老阿嘛？大撚把呀<br />\n成撚日淨係識打飛機<br />\n革你老味<br />\n一味唸住靠英國靠美國幫<br />\n完全冇醒悟到香港人係要靠自己<br />\n憑咩講時代革命呀你老味<br />\n親如英國佬由佔中開始到依家都係強烈譴責完就89798<br />\n強如美國佬你以為trump冇利益關係會出聲咩<br />\n屌你老味一路以黎連登仔所有嘅貢獻大家有目共睹<br />\n但成熟少少得唔撚得呀<br />\n再咁搞落去亦唔會再有外國人去支持<br />\n核彈都唔割？未核彈之前都就黎成盤散沙啦<br />\n成撚日唸住靠其他國家勢力<br />\n人地肯出聲已經係要感恩戴德啦<br />\n醒未阿你班仆街<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">時代革命係香港人要自己靠自己阿<br />\n唔撚係鳩叫口號呀大佬<br />\n香港人真係加油啦好唔撚好</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d40b2ee777548147d6e088d48e25350decbadd68","tid":1537780,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:57:26.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d9343f67b894221a689b22a15dc47f29453ffe91","tid":1537780,"uid":120279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:14:34.000Z","msg":"岩啊！仲要成日都話攬炒 大家幾時先肯行多一步？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"481864a0e94a9a37cdb8ddfa37c4eb045051e970","tid":1537780,"uid":120279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"十連推 1/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabe6fc646d530c1c37638619d5cfaca17718737","tid":1537780,"uid":120279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:17:47.000Z","msg":"十連推 2/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0847399d63736a823e7966924132e25e7a3b9508","tid":1537780,"uid":120279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:18:04.000Z","msg":"十連推 3/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10a8e68704cfeafb485f9a55751c51803b50f993","tid":1537780,"uid":120279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T05:18:23.000Z","msg":"十連推 4/10 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"